19:01.240 --> 19:06.200
<i>♪ Everybody's gotta</i>
<i>Get out of the city ♪</i>

19:12.480 --> 19:13.680
<i>♪ Hah! ♪</i>

19:20.560 --> 19:22.560
<i>♪ Now I'm livin' in the city</i>
<i>Where the scenery is pretty ♪</i>

